STATE of North Carolina
v.
Vincent INGLE. No. 335P01-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 3, 2005. Vincent Ingle, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Anne M. Middleton, Assistant Attorney General, Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 26th day of October 2004 by Defendant in this matter for discretionary review, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 3rd day of February 2005."
